# yamls/us/reloc_*.yml are now COMMITTED. They're regenerated from
# tools/reloc_data_symbols.us.txt + ROM by tools/generate_yamls.py;
# regen and re-commit when reloc_data_symbols.us.txt changes (rare for
# a frozen v1.0). Same pattern as port/resource/RelocFileTable.cpp.
# Their content (file_id ↔ symbol ↔ ROM offset/size) is a strict
# subset of upstream ssb-decomp-re's smashbrothers.us.yaml splat
# config — standard decomp metadata, no ROM bytes.

